NAME
    Hopkins::Plugin::HMI - hopkins HMI session (using HTTP)

DESCRIPTION
    Hopkins::Plugin::HMI encapsulates the HMI (human machine interface) POE
    session created by the manager session. this session uses the
    Server::HTTP component to provide a web interface to the job server
    using Catalyst.

STATES
    new

AUTHOR
    Mike Eldridge <diz@cpan.org>

